クラス ThresholdSha256Fulfillment

    public class ThresholdSha256Fulfillment
extends FulfillmentBase<ThresholdSha256Condition>
implements Fulfillment<ThresholdSha256Condition>
    An implementation of Fulfillment for a crypto-condition fulfillment of type "THRESHOLD-SHA-256" based upon a number of sub-conditions and sub-fulfillments.
    関連項目:
    "https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-thomas-crypto-conditions/"

    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • ThresholdSha256Fulfillment

        public ThresholdSha256Fulfillment(List<Condition> subconditions,
                                  List<Fulfillment> subfulfillments)
        Required-args Constructor. In order to create a threshold fulfillment,
        パラメータ:
        subconditions - An ordered List of unfulfilled sub-conditions that correspond to the threshold condition being fulfilled. For example, if a given Threshold condition has 2 preimage sub-conditions, but a threshold of 1, then a valid fulfillment would have one of those preimage conditions in this List, and a fulfillment for the other preimage condition in the fulfillments list. Note that this list must be combined with the list of conditions derived from the subfulfillments, and the combined list, sorted, is used as the value when deriving the fingerprint of this threshold fulfillment.
        subfulfillments - An ordered List of fulfillments. The number of elements in this list is equal to the threshold of this fulfillment (i.e., per the crypto-condtions specification, implementations must use the length of this list as the threshold value when deriving the fingerprint of this crypto-condition).

      • verify

        public boolean verify(ThresholdSha256Condition condition,
                      byte[] message)

        Verify the THRESHOLD-SHA-256.

        A THRESHOLD-SHA-256 fulfillment is valid iff:

        1. 1. All (F).subfulfillments are valid.
        2. 2. The derived condition (D) (found in condition) is equal to the given condition (C).

        For more general details about Fulfillment validation, see the Javadoc in Fulfillment.verify(Condition, byte[]).

        定義:
        verify インタフェース内 Fulfillment<ThresholdSha256Condition>
        パラメータ:
        condition - A Condition that this fulfillment should verify.
        message - A byte array that is part of verifying the supplied condition.
        戻り値:
        true if the condition validates this fulfillment; false otherwise.
        関連項目:
        "https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-thomas-crypto-conditions-03#section-5"
